FBIS4-48119 "drafr092_c_94015" FBIS-AFR-94-092 Daily Report 12 May 1994 REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA W. Transvaal ANC Welcomes Verdict W. Transvaal ANC Welcomes Verdict MB1205075594 Johannesburg SAPA in English 0719 GMT 12 May 94 MB1205075594 Johannesburg SAPA English BFN [Text] Klerksdorp May 12 SAPA -- The African National Congress' Western Transvaal region on Thursday [12 May] welcomed the verdict handed down on six rightwingers sentenced to death for the killing of four black people on the West Rand last year. A statement issued on Thursday said: "Although the ANC is opposed to capital punishment, we welcome the verdict handed down by the court and hope that this will serve as a deterrent to other rightwingers who were bent on creating havoc in this province."
